<pb ed="T" id="T20.1160.0660b" n="0660b"/>
<lb n="0660b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0660b02"/><head type="no">No. 1160</head>
<lb n="0660b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0660001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>日光菩薩月光菩薩陀羅尼<note place="inline">此&CB00057;出觀世音菩薩
<lb n="0660b04"/>大悲心陀羅尼經</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0660b05"/>
<lb n="0660b06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>日光菩薩。為受持大悲心陀羅尼者。說大神
<lb n="0660b07"/>&CB00057;。而擁護<note n="0660002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（即說&CB00057;曰）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0660002"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">之即說&CB00057;曰</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0660b08"/><p type="dharani">南無勃陀瞿<note place="inline">上聲</note>那<note place="inline">上聲</note>迷<note place="inline">一</note>南無達摩莫訶
<lb n="0660b09"/><note n="0660003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">低＝室&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0660003"><lem>低</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">室</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note>南無僧伽多夜泥<note place="inline">三</note>底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>哩部畢<note place="inline">四</note>薩
<lb n="0660b10"/><note place="inline">僧沒切</note>咄<note place="inline">登沒切</note>擔納摩<note place="inline">五</note>娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0660b11"/><p>誦此&CB00057;滅一切罪。亦能辟魔及除天災。若誦
<lb n="0660b12"/>一遍禮佛一拜。如是日別三時誦&CB00057;禮佛。未
<lb n="0660b13"/>來之世所受身處。<note n="0660004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0660004"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">常</rdg></app>得一一相貌端正具足
<lb n="0660b14"/>果報</p>
<lb n="0660b15"/><p>月光菩薩亦為誦持大悲心陀羅尼者。說大
<lb n="0660b16"/>神&CB00057;為諸行人說。陀羅尼&CB00057;而擁護之。即說
<lb n="0660b17"/>&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0660b18"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0660005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">深＝具&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0660005"><lem>深</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">具</rdg></app>低帝屠蘇吒<note place="inline">一</note>阿若密<note n="0660006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＝吒&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0660006"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">吒</rdg></app>烏都吒<note place="inline">二</note>深耆
<lb n="0660b19"/>吒<note place="inline">三</note>波賴帝吒<note place="inline">四</note>耶彌若吒烏都吒<note place="inline">五</note>拘羅帝
<lb n="0660b20"/>吒<note n="0660007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（闍）&M062403;＋耆【原】</note><app n="0660007"><lem>耆</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">闍耆</rdg></app>摩吒<note place="inline">六</note>娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0660b21"/><p>誦此&CB00057;五遍。取五色線作&CB00057;索。痛處繫此&CB00057;。
<lb n="0660b22"/>乃是過去四十&M010527;河沙諸佛所說。我今亦說。
<lb n="0660b23"/>為諸行人作擁護故。除一切障難故。除一切
<lb n="0660b24"/>惡病<note n="0660008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔痛〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0660008"><lem>痛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>故。成就一切諸善法故。遠離一切諸
<lb n="0660b25"/>怖畏故。若有謗此&CB00057;者即為謗彼諸佛</p><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
<lb n="0660b26"/><div1 type="W"><p>貞享三年丙寅九月二十二夕一校了</p>
<lb n="0660b27"/><p>　　　　　　　　　　　　淨嚴<note place="inline">四十八</note></p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
